Introduction

SWEET:CH is a seven-member boy group under DNA Entertainment and DND ENS. They made their debut on April 20, 2025.

In April of 2024, DNA Entertainment opened up SNS accounts for their upcoming boy group SWEET:CH. Originally set to debut in August 2024, it was revealed in January, 2025 that their debut had been pushed to the first half of the new year. A few days later, it was announced that the group would release a pre-debut single in February.
